{"tid":1485970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼帶來的傷害比鬼本身大 10,000 倍","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T19:06:20.000Z","uid":46422,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"77ddf0846b0ed43ea5776cf397c2da4c39fb6cee","tid":1485970,"uid":46422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"今日好多人話金鐘唔走就係鬼。<br />\n<br />\n今朝先讃完嘅冇分和勇瞬間忘記咗<br />\n<br />\n前線有鬼係一定<br />\n<br />\n但係你細心啲諗下佢做得啲乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最多咪又係放火燒下雜物。 比到盡 cocktail 差館好未<br />\n<br />\n驚失去本地中立派支持嘅，呢堆野之前一早做咗，今日都有170萬人出嚟你驚啲乜。<br />\n<br />\n驚係失去國際支持嘅，你唔好當嗰啲外國人特別係記者同嗰啲冇腦藍絲廢老一樣得唔得<br />\n<br />\n有咁多片見到警方喬裝示威者，你有嘅懷疑佢哋一樣會有<br />\n<br />\n每個策略都有佢嘅弱點，但係唔代表嗰個策略係錯。無需追求贏得完美無瑕，淨係需要贏<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割呢個策略，弱點就係你要承受鬼做嘅嘢，警察只不過係好正路咁樣運用呢個弱點。<br />\n<br />\n但係呢個策略帶來的好處，係我哋運動能夠持續到而家, 全民connect<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記警察用呢個策略亦有巨大嘅風險，布袋彈有機會射倒自己夥計，燒緊隻鬼亦有機會俾人周到正一正，冇得否認<br />\n<br />\n調轉頭諗如果我哋轉用 bb 彈都割，警察就唔使咁曬心機派鬼，留喺差館un un腳等你自己內控搞掂， 0 風險。<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，鬼做嘅任何野都唔會有自己捉鬼所帶來的傷害咁大。<br />\n<br />\n如果你認同我講嘅嘢請你幫手推一推，唔想再見到出面全部都係留喺度就係鬼，勇武搞鑊哂嘅 post。"},{"pid":"338272b7c434349a1fcd37c23eed125be2c50f81","tid":1485970,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"㩒錢/換美金，經濟戰未完"},{"pid":"a8d952a23682cb04127ad3ab40a5675b24b49c4a","tid":1485970,"uid":38464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"完全認同 幫推"},{"pid":"ded545aaebf098b1b1e07d8af91e6266404079af","tid":1485970,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMjntZZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMjntZZ.jpg&h=25eeebc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c483e7e28032e327f7b354921480cfb276a2d8c","tid":1485970,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:31:31.000Z","msg":"不割蓆(主要係5毛手段)係指同路人<br />\n不包括有心搞事製做事端e.g,  8.11銅羅灣事件，77盧溝橋事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冷靜，小心又被騎劫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXjR6MO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXjR6MO.gif&h=453f1ea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33a89b46c69903320a73d0a65f935cb38dd61f4c","tid":1485970,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UbhhTw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UbhhTw.jpg&h=776a7625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99U6VFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99U6VFb.jpg&h=3f996fec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de697ed855aa08d42081d5388148e5e5854a8063","tid":1485970,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下墜之瓜，何堪再摘</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qkKOhrf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqkKOhrf.png&h=b8d97334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3kE8xY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3kE8xY.jpg&h=9da784d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7474e5d4479885f8800cdb3aa1e2e6f35cbe1c74","tid":1485970,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"仲上緊警嫂嘅手足把握時間呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa98439d9c21d0ebfd7a9be564ff72cc34b23a26","tid":1485970,"uid":48427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e233b2680b69b1db171577e4f43d2231ffe2d1b8","tid":1485970,"uid":85812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"認同，幫推<br />\n<br />\n警察派鬼混入示威者，唔係第一日嘅事。但當佢打開口牌，大家就自亂陣腳。<br />\n<br />\n任何勇武行動無論係前線做定鬼做，大家只須支持同幫手拆局。"},{"pid":"d59c9c09b5f5cd849c875ea2116bc1aa3040721a","tid":1485970,"uid":278759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"唯有全盤接受，先至可以解決『鬼』嘅問題<br />\n『鬼』所做嘅嘢，你跟住做又走得甩，咁有冇『鬼』都唔成問題<br />\n但同樣，既然係『全盤接受』，咁點解唔可以全盤接受做一次『戰略性退卻』？等對家知悉我哋每一場運動都有可進可退嘅方案。<br />\n我哋知道有『鬼』嘅時候，可以全退。我哋知道冇『鬼』嘅時候，可以全進。咁先至係可以撚到狗"},{"pid":"b4084ed11e0f1bb390a4b40ac28f20e67fd3ce3f","tid":1485970,"uid":278759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d59c9c09b5f5cd849c875ea2116bc1aa3040721a","tid":1485970,"uid":278759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"唯有全盤接受，先至可以解決『鬼』嘅問題<br />\n『鬼』所做嘅嘢，你跟住做又走得甩，咁有冇『鬼』都唔成問題<br />\n但同樣，既然係『全盤接受』，咁點解唔可以全盤接受做一次『戰略性退卻』？等對家知悉我哋每一場運動都有可進可退嘅方案。<br />\n我哋知道有『鬼』嘅時候，可以全退。我哋知道冇『鬼』嘅時候，可以全進。咁先至係可以撚到狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"再進化，就係<br />\n我哋知道有『鬼』嘅時候，都可以全進。我哋知道冇『鬼』嘅時候，都可以全退。"},{"pid":"40bee1d55f63fdb7ea656e16dd9b990f8102b8b7","tid":1485970,"uid":46422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c483e7e28032e327f7b354921480cfb276a2d8c","tid":1485970,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:31:31.000Z","msg":"不割蓆(主要係5毛手段)係指同路人<br />\n不包括有心搞事製做事端e.g,  8.11銅羅灣事件，77盧溝橋事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冷靜，小心又被騎劫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXjR6MO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXjR6MO.gif&h=453f1ea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:44:17.000Z","msg":"有心搞事製造事端，唔會係個額頭上面刻着俾你睇<br />\n<br />\n你要搵佢哋出嚟就先要捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n本文標題：捉鬼所帶來的傷害比鬼本身能夠做到嘅傷害大一萬倍<br />\n<br />\n鬼究竟做啲乜嘢，可以比我哋互相指責互相猜疑所帶來的傷害更大<br />\n<br />\n請你明白 「核彈都唔割」呢個策略唔係完美，有佢嘅弱點。 但我確信呢個係最有可能帶來勝利嘅策略。"},{"pid":"70806fded20363718094691d53dabfd1a5d12038","tid":1485970,"uid":80125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98cd43e661bc9e1bfaa8a5d73de6e8ea2dfd2a3d","tid":1485970,"uid":21883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:57:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4deaa6d7852b28f42a24a3a2ed161c1c8cdec1af","tid":1485970,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:58:13.000Z","msg":"機場嗰仗怨氣好大<br />\n不斷係到捉鬼前線又屌黎屌去<br />\n到阻塞旅客嗰到爆得最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c419d4391c3b8b3626f39153a61e80801de1ef80","tid":1485970,"uid":227735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"勇武巴出位少少又話係鬼 咁捉鬼同割席有咩分別 <br />\n前線做嘢唔認同可以唔主動幫 真係覺得唔合理可以幫手拆<br />\n唯獨唔好製造恐慌 自亂陣腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2fa60679d12ccc223100a087668421817b3dc2","tid":1485970,"uid":227735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:16:20.000Z","msg":"再講真係俾你捉到又可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通當場打死佢咩 最後咪又係放佢走<br />\n仲要前提係有reliable方法可以捉到真鬼 以誤傷友軍同製造無謂恐慌 又浪費自己友心力嚟搵所謂嘅鬼我覺得唔抵"},{"pid":"995e27c7dce1ca47c32df91540b2a1bf4d992f42","tid":1485970,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"光復連登<br />\n5毛出post大量討論"}]}